    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> meat-free mince</strong> with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>then<strong> </strong>cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to brown all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
